<H3> <TI>   TRETYE SOSLOVIYE Resumes Publication </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    TRETYE SOSLOVIYE Resumes Publication </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM2004093994 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 16 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> PM2004093994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow IZVESTIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
