<H3> <TI>   Deputy Premier on Money Merger Ratification </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deputy Premier on Money Merger Ratification </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS1904133694 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1000 
GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS1904133694 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk Radio Minsk Network </F>
<F P=105>  Belarusian </F>


<TEXT>
