<DOCNO> FBIS4-16822 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drsov076_a_94019" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-SOV-94-076 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  19 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Further Reportage on PLO Chairman 'Arafat's Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Further Reportage on PLO Chairman 'Arafat's Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Meets With Patriarch Aleksiy </H4>

<F P=102> LD1904181894 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
1600 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1904181894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vesti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Patriarch Aleksiy II of Moscow and All Russia today 
received PLO leader Yasir 'Arafat at his residence in St. 
Daniil's Monastery. In his introductory speech, 'Arafat said 
that the relations connecting our countries are very stable and 
friendly, and that he sees Russia as an example of great 
humanism. After his introductory speech, the press were asked 
to leave and the talks were continued behind closed doors. 

</TEXT>

