<H3> <TI>   Clash With Militants on Afghan Border Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Clash With Militants on Afghan Border Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2004085094 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0725 
GMT 20 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2004085094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] </F>
  [Text] Dushanbe, 20 Apr -- Last night a group of Tajik 
opposition militants attempted to break through from Afghanistan 
to Tajikistan in one of the sectors covered by the Pyandzh 
border guards. In the course of a short armed clash between the 
militants and the Russian border guards, one of the 
transgressors was killed and the rest returned to the Afghan 
bank of the Pyandzh. All was quiet last night on all the other 
areas of the Tajik-Afghan border. This information was given to 
an ITAR-TASS correspondent at the headquarters of the Russian 
border troops in Tajikistan. 

</TEXT>

