  [Excerpts] Li Peng, chairman of the State Council of the 
People's Republic of China, arrived in Tashkent yesterday [18 
April] on an official visit. Uzbek President Islam Karimov and 
his wife met Li Peng and his wife at the airport. [passage 
omitted on reception ceremony] 
  In his speech at the airport the Chinese leader said: I am 
very happy about my visit to Tashkent, the most ancient and 
