the night of 17 April. They also engaged large infantry units 
in the fighting. Violent clashes took place until 0800 this 
morning, 18 April. The enemy's onslaught was obstructed and 
[words indistinct]. Five Armenian tanks, a PDM [expansion 
unknown], and some 90 enemy troops were destroyed in the 
