<H3> <TI>   Bomb Found on Baku Train, 2 Suspects Detained </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bomb Found on Baku Train, 2 Suspects Detained </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1904183094 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1904183094 </F>
<F P=104>  Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network </F>

<F P=105>  Azeri </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] According to information provided by the National 
Security Ministry, a high-powered explosive device in a 
cardboard box was found and defused on the No. 5 Baku-to-Moscow 
passenger train during a joint search by the employees of the 
republic's National Security Ministry and the Interior Ministry 
at Baku train station some days ago. Two citizens suspected of 
the sabotage act were detained. The National Security 
Ministry's investigation department has instituted criminal 
proceedings and launched an investigation. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

