<H3> <TI>   Prisoners of War Exchanged With Abkhazia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Prisoners of War Exchanged With Abkhazia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1904120994 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1000 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1904120994 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>
<F P=105>  Georgian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Zugdidi, 19 Apr -- An IBERIA correspondent reports 
that a meeting was held on 18 April between the Rescue Corps' 
commission for the exchange of prisoners of war and Abkhaz 
representatives. The Georgian delegation included commission 
leader Paata Zakareishvili and Gia Baramidze, a deputy in the 
Georgian Parliament. The meeting was held in a calm atmosphere. 
An exchange of prisoners took place. 
  The Georgian side would like to thank the Abkhaz 
representatives, especially Rusudan Kishmaria and Vitaliy 
Adleiba, for their contribution to the success of the meeting. 

