<F P=102>   LD1904174394 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1300 GMT 
19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1904174394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


