<F P=100> Moldova </F>
<H3> <TI>   Snegur Signs Decree on Enterprise Debt Payments </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Snegur Signs Decree on Enterprise Debt Payments </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2004160894 Chisinau BASAPRESS in English 1945 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU2004160894 </F>
<F P=104>  Chisinau BASAPRESS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Chisinau BASAPRESS, 19/4/1994 -- President Mircea 
Snegur signed today a decree on paying off the arrears and 
stabilizing the financial situation of Moldovan enterprises and 
organizations. According to the decree, the National Bank and 
commercial banks will compensate the mutual debts using the 
financial means of the enterprises and organizations and 
budgetary means as well. The Republican and local commissions 
must compile by 15 May the list of the enterprises with debts 
and deposit and hard currency accounts opened in the Moldovan 
commercial banks and abroad; they must count the sums thus 
deposited. They will have to count the sums of unrepatriated 
hard currency for the export of goods and services. According 
to the decree, the Ministry of Finance, the State Central Fiscal 
Inspectorate and the Financial Guard will levy the delayed 
payments to the budget from the enterprises' hard currency 
accounts. The state enterprises and organizations were allowed 
to sell at auctions as IOU's their debts. According to sources 
from the Ministry of Finance the mutual debts are over 400-500 
million lei. 

</TEXT>

