<H3> <TI>   New Administrative Territorial Unit Created </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Administrative Territorial Unit Created </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2004180294 Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network in 
Russian 2300 GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2004180294 </F>
<F P=104>  Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Zhogorku Kenesh adopted a resolution to unite 
the city of Tokmak with Chuyskiy Rayon and the city of Naryn 
with Tianshanskiy Rayon into a single administrative unit. The 
deputies believe this merger to be expedient and in all respects 
positive. The bureaucratic staff will be reduced, management of 
the national economy in the region will be focused on the one 
hand, agrarians will be more interested in supplying the urban 
area with food in order to receive industrial goods in return. 

</TEXT>

