<F P=102>   NC2004140694 Yerevan SNARK in English 0803 GMT 20 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2004140694 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Stepanakert, April 20 (SNARK)--Today morning, after 
intensive artillery shelling, the units of Azerbaijani army 
passed to offensive at south-eastern sector of 
Karabakh-Azerbaijan front. Press-service of Karabakh Defence 
Army informs, a great number of military hardware and infantry 
is taking part in the offensive. According to data received by 
midday, there are stubborn fightings at this sector, and both of 
the sides have losses. 
  Today, it is calm at the others sectors of the front, 
including southern part of Mardakertskiy region where there have 
been furious fightings for the last ten days. 

</TEXT>

