Belgrade, and the holding of an international conference on a 
Bosnian settlement, of which Russia was the initiator, were 
touched upon during the course of the telephone conversation. 
  In connection with his conversation with B. Yeltsin, the 
U.S. 
President postponed a news conference in the White House, 
earlier scheduled for 2300 Moscow time, by one hour. 

